snippet.title: Diana and Roma How to behave in a hotel / Rules of conduct for kids
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma settled in a hotel in Dubai. Children play and play a little hooligan. Mom and dad explain to Diana and Roma how to behave in a hotel. Simple rules of conduct for kids
